# Template for local `wrangler dev`. Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored) and fill in a real
# key locally. NEVER commit .dev.vars or a real key. In production this is a wrangler secret:
#   wrangler secret put ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY="<your-anthropic-api-key>"
# EVM private key hex for PoL DataItem signing (devnet: throwaway, faucet-funded).
# Production: wrangler secret put IRYS_UPLOAD_KEY
IRYS_UPLOAD_KEY="<evm-private-key-hex>"
# Dedicated MAINNET Irys signing key (mainnet path, 2026-07-14). Holds REAL Base
# ETH; fund with pol-irys-fund.ts --node mainnet; prove with pol-mainnet-anchor.ts.
# In production this key becomes the IRYS_UPLOAD_KEY secret when IRYS_NODE_URL
# flips to uploader.irys.xyz. Kept SEPARATE from the devnet throwaway on purpose.
IRYS_MAINNET_KEY="<evm-private-key-hex>"
# Payer-side burner for the x402 rehearsal harness (pol-paid-call.ts) ONLY.
# Holds base-sepolia USDC; gas is facilitator-paid. NEVER a Worker secret.
X402_PAYER_KEY="<evm-private-key-hex>"
# CDP facilitator credentials (A10). Server-side SECRETS, read request-scoped.
# CDP Secret API key with NO Coinbase App scopes (View/Trade/Transfer/Receive
# all OFF); it only authenticates JWT requests to the x402 platform API.
# Production: wrangler secret put CDP_API_KEY_ID / CDP_API_KEY_SECRET
CDP_API_KEY_ID="<cdp-api-key-id>"
CDP_API_KEY_SECRET="<cdp-api-key-secret>"
# Dedicated on-chain trust-score writer (Phase 3). A NEW key, authorized via
# authorizeWriter() from the contract owner, funded with a little Base ETH for
# gas. NOT the owner key. Absent => on-chain scoring is skipped (audits/certs
# unaffected). Production: wrangler secret put DJZS_WRITER_KEY
DJZS_WRITER_KEY="<evm-private-key-hex>"
# Optional Base RPC for the score write; defaults to https://mainnet.base.org.
# BASE_RPC_URL="https://..."
# DJZS subgraph GraphQL query URL (Phase 3) for query_agent_trust. The Graph
# Studio dev URL carries an API key, so treat it as a SECRET. Absent =>
# query_agent_trust reports "unavailable". Production: wrangler secret put SUBGRAPH_URL
SUBGRAPH_URL="<graph-studio-query-url>"
